MG_KEGS_WATERFALLS_2025


Version 1.0 Initial Release :

- New, original and more modernized version of the map mg_kegs_course_v3_fixed
- The map design has been revamped with more modern textures
- Traps in the third and fourth rooms have been replaced with new ones
- 30-second respawn delay has been disabled
- 20-second countdown before the end of the game when someone finishes the course
- Map fully checked and tested
- Total of 10 Traps and one secret room

MG_KEGS_WATERFALLS_HARD


Version 1.0 Initial Release :

- More difficult version of the map mg_kegs_waterfalls_2025
- The map design has been revamped with more modern textures
- Traps in the third and fourth rooms have been replaced with new ones
- 30-second respawn delay has been disabled
- 20-second countdown before the end of the game when someone finishes the course
- Map fully checked and tested
- Total of 18 Traps and one secret room
